::DarkMouse::

She leaned against him.  She liked being that close to him. When he hugged 
her, she felt his strength and it filled her with warmth. She kissed him and 
looked at him. She smiled, "I love you too."
She rested her head on his shoulder.  It made her feel good to be with him.  
She knew not where these feelings came from or how they got inside her, but 
she was pleased that she had them. And even more pleased that she had them 
for Scorponok.
She felt like something inside was filled.  She loved him and didn't ever 
want him to leave. She looked at him and stroked her hand against his cheek. 
She fell in love with everything about him.
